  <p>
    A more detailed tutorial of how to install a CA certificate can be
    found <%= link_to 'here', 'http://wiki.cacert.org/wiki/BrowserClients' %>. When it asks you to download a
    certificate or click on a link for one, substitute the above link.
  </p>
  <hr />


  <h3>Important</h3>
